securities and exchange commission under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, issued, insured, or guaranteed by the United States; by a state; by a political subdivision of a state; by a public authority, agency, or instrumentality of one or more states; by a political subdivision of one or more states; or by a person controlled or supervised by and acting as an instrumentality of the United States under authority granted by the Congress; or a certificate of deposit for any of the foregoing.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E5_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E5_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Foreign government securities.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A security issued, insured, or guaranteed by a foreign government with which the United States maintains diplomatic relations, or any of its political subdivisions, if the security is recognized as a valid obligation by the issuer, insurer, or guarantor.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E6_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E6_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Depository institution and international banking institution securities.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A security issued by and representing or that will represent an interest in or a direct obligation of, or be guaranteed by any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An international banking institution.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A banking institution organized under the laws of the United States; a member bank of the United States federal reserve system; or a depository institution, a substantial portion of the business of which consists or will consist of receiving deposits or share accounts that are insured to the maximum amount authorized by statute by the federal deposit insurance corporation, the national credit union share insurance fund, or a successor authorized by federal law or exercising fiduciary powers that are similar to those permitted for national banks under the authority of the comptroller of the currency pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Pub. L. No. 87-722, \'a71}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{12 U.S.C. \'a792a}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Any other depository institution, unless by rule or order the administrator proceeds under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 502.204}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{4.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E7_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E7_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Insurance company securities.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A security issued by and representing an interest in, or a debt of, or insured or guaranteed by, an insurance company authorized to do business in this state.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{5.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E8_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E8_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Common carrier and public utility securities.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A security issued or guaranteed by a railroad, other common carrier, public utility, or public utility holding company that is any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Regulated in respect to its rates and charges by the United States or a state.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Regulated in respect to the issuance or guarantee of the security by the United States, a state, Canada, or a Canadian province or territory.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A public utility holding company registered under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Public Utility Holding Company Act of 1935}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or a subsidiary of such a registered holding company within the meaning of that Act.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{6.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E9_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E9_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Certain options and rights.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A federal covered security specified in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 18(b)(1) of the Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{15 U.S.C. \'a777r(b)(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or by rule adopted under that provision or a security listed or approved for listing on another securities market specified by rule under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; a put or a call option contract; a warrant; a subscription right on or with respect to such securities; or an option or similar derivative security on a security or an index of securities or foreign currencies issued by a clearing agency registered under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Exchange Act of 1934}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and listed or designated for trading on a national securities exchange, a facility of a national securities exchange, or a facility of a national securities association registered under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Exchange Act of 1934}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or an offer or sale, of the underlying security in connection with the offer, sale, or exercise of an option or other security that was exempt when the option or other security was written or issued; or an option or a derivative security designated by the securities and exchange commission under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 9(b) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{15 U.S.C. \'a778i(b)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{7.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E1_30_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E1_30_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Nonprofit securities.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A security issued by a person organized and operated exclusively for religious, educational, benevolent, fraternal, charitable, social, athletic, or reformatory purposes, or as a chamber of commerce, and not for pecuniary profit, no part of the net earnings of which inures to the benefit of a private stockholder or other person, or a security of a company that is excluded from the definition of an investment company under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 3(c)(10)(B) of the Investment Company Act of 1940}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{15 U.S.C. \'a780a-3(c)(10)(B)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; except that with respect to the offer or sale of a note, bond, debenture, or other evidence of indebtedness issued by such a person, a rule may be adopted under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ limiting the availability of this exemption by classifying securities, persons, and transactions, imposing different requirements for different classes, specifying with respect to paragraph }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fb\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ the scope of the exemption and the grounds for denial or suspension, and requiring an issuer to do any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{File a notice specifying the material terms of the proposed offer or sale and copies of any proposed sales and advertising literature to be used and provide that the exemption becomes effective if the administrator does not disallow the exemption within the period established by the rule.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{File a request for exemption authorization for which a rule under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ may specify the scope of the exemption, the requirement of an offering statement, the filing of sales and advertising literature, the filing of consent to service of process complying with }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 502.611}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, and grounds for denial or suspension of the exemption.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Register under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 502.304}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{8.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Reserved.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{8A.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E12_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E12_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Cooperative associations.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A stock or similar security, including a patronage refund certificate, issued by any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A cooperative housing corporation described in paragraph 1 of subsection }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fb\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 216 of the Internal Revenue Code}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, if its activities are limited to the ownership, leasing, management, or construction of residential properties for its members, and activities incidental thereto.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A mutual or cooperative organization, including a cooperative association organized in good faith under and for any of the purposes enumerated in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 497}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{498}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{499}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{501}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{501A}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, that deals in commodities or supplies goods or services in transactions primarily with and for the benefit of its members, if all of the following apply:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Such stock or similar security is part of a class issuable only to persons who deal in commodities with, or obtain goods or services from, the issuer.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Such stock or similar security is transferable only to the issuer or a successor in interest of the transferor who qualifies for membership in such mutual or cooperative organization.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{No dividends other than patronage refunds are payable to holders of such stock or similar security except on a complete or partial liquidation.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{8B.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E13_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E13_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Agricultural cooperative associations.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A security issued by an agricultural cooperative association, provided all of the following conditions are satisfied:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A commission or remuneration must not be paid or provided either directly or indirectly for the sale, except as permitted by the administrator by rule or by order issued upon written application showing good cause for allowance of a commission or other remuneration.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the securities to be issued are notes or other evidences of indebtedness and are issued after July 1, 1991, the issuer must file with the administrator a written notice specifying the name of the issuer, the date of the issuer\u8217\'3fs organization, the name of a contact person, a copy of the issuer\u8217\'3fs current audited financial statement, the types of security or securities to be offered, and the class of persons to whom the offer will be made in accordance with such rules as prescribed by the administrator.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{9.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E14_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E14_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Equipment trust certificate.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An equipment trust certificate with respect to equipment leased or conditionally sold to a person, if any security issued by the person would be exempt under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or would be a federal covered security under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 18(b)(1) of the Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{15 U.S.C. \'a777r(b)(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{9A.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E15_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E15_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Economic development corporations.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Any security issued by a corporation formed under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 496B}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{9B.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E16_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E16_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ Iowa finance authority.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Any security issued by the Iowa finance authority under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 16, subchapter VIII}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{9C.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E17_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E17_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Membership campgrounds.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Any security representing a membership camping contract which is registered pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 557B.2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or exempt under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 557B.4}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{9D.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E18_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E18_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Time-shares.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Any security representing a time-share interval as defined in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 557A.2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{9E.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E19_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E2_2E19_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Viatical settlement investment contracts.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A viatical settlement investment contract, or fractional or pooled interest in such contract, provided any of the following conditions are satisfied:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The assignment, transfer, sale, devise, or bequest of a death benefit of a life insurance policy or contract is made by the viator to an insurance company as provided under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Title XIII, subtitle 1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The assignment, transfer, sale, devise, or bequest of a life insurance policy or contract, for any value less than the expected death benefit, is made by the viator to a family member or other person who enters into no more than one such agreement in a calendar year.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A life insurance policy or contract is assigned to a bank, savings bank, savings and loan association, credit union, or other licensed lending institution as collateral for a loan.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Accelerated benefits are exercised as provided in the life insurance policy or contract and consistent with applicable law.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{e.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The assignment, transfer, sale, devise, or bequest of the death benefit or ownership of a life insurance policy or contract made by the policyholder or contract owner to a viatical settlement provider, if the viatical settlement transaction complies with }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 508E}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, including rules adopted pursuant to that chapter.}}}\par}{}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{[C31, 35, \'a78581-c6; C39, \'a7}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{8581.06;}}}{ C46, 50, 54, 58, 62, 66, 71, 73, 75, \'a7502.6; C77, 79, }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{81, \'a7502.201}}}{]}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{97 Acts, ch 114, \'a75}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2004 Acts, ch 1161, \'a75, 68}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2006 Acts, ch 1117, \'a77}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2008 Acts, ch 1123, \'a71}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2013 Acts, ch 100, \'a726, 27}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2014 Acts, ch 1080, \'a793, 98}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0\cbpat2{Referred to in }{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{\'a7502.203}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 502.204}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 502.301}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 502.302}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 502.504}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 557B.14}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\sb219\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{ }{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{502.202}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E2_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E2_2E2}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Exempt transactions.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{The following transactions are exempt from the requirements of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{sections 502.301 through 502.306}}}{ and }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{502.504}}}{:}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{1.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E4_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E4_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Isolated nonissuer transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An isolated nonissuer transaction, whether effected by or through a broker-dealer or not.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E5_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E5_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Nonissuer transactions in specified outstanding securities.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nonissuer transaction by or through a broker-dealer registered, or exempt from registration, under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, and a resale transaction by a sponsor of a unit investment trust registered under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Investment Company Act of 1940}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, provided that for either transaction, the security is of a class that has been outstanding in the hands of the public for at least ninety days, if, at the date of the transaction, all of the following apply:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The issuer of the security is engaged in business, the issuer is not in the organizational stage or in bankruptcy or receivership, and the issuer is not a blank check, blind pool, or shell company that has no specific business plan or purpose or has indicated that its primary business plan is to engage in a merger or combination of the business with, or an acquisition of, an unidentified person.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The security is sold at a price reasonably related to its current market price.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The security does not constitute the whole or part of an unsold allotment to, or a subscription or participation by, the broker-dealer as an underwriter of the security, or a redistribution.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nationally recognized securities manual or its electronic equivalent designated by rule adopted or order issued under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or a record filed with the securities and exchange commission that is publicly available contains all of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A description of the business and operations of the issuer.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The names of the issuer\u8217\'3fs executive officers and the names of the issuer\u8217\'3fs directors, if any.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An audited balance sheet of the issuer as of a date within eighteen months before the date of the transaction or, in the case of a reorganization or merger when the parties to the reorganization or merger each had an audited balance sheet, and a pro forma balance sheet for the combined organization.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(4)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An audited income statement for each of the issuer\u8217\'3fs two immediately previous fiscal years or for the period of existence of the issuer, whichever is shorter, or, in the case of a reorganization or merger when each party to the reorganization or merger had audited income statements, and a pro forma income statement.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{e.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Any one of the following requirements is met:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The issuer of the security has a class of equity securities listed on a national securities exchange registered under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 6 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The issuer of the security is a unit investment trust registered under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Investment Company Act of 1940}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The issuer of the security, including its predecessors, has been engaged in continuous business for at least three years.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(4)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The issuer of the security has total assets of at least two million dollars based on an audited balance sheet as of a date within eighteen months before the date of the transaction or, in the case of a reorganization or merger when the parties to the reorganization or merger each had such an audited balance sheet, and a pro forma balance sheet for the combined organization.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E6_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E6_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Nonissuer transactions in specified foreign transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nonissuer transaction by or through a broker-dealer registered or exempt from registration under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ in a security of a foreign issuer that is a margin security defined in regulations or rules adopted by the board of governors of the United States federal reserve system.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{4.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E7_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E7_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Nonissuer transactions in securities subject to securities exchange act reporting.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nonissuer transaction by or through a broker-dealer registered or exempt from registration under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ in an outstanding security if the guarantor of the security files reports with the securities and exchange commission under the reporting requirements of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 13 or 15(d) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{15 U.S.C. \'a778m or 78o(d)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{5.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E8_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E8_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Nonissuer transactions in specified fixed income securities.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nonissuer transaction by or through a broker-dealer registered or exempt from registration under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ in a security if any of the following apply:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{It is rated at the time of the transaction by a nationally recognized statistical rating organization in one of its four highest rating categories.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{It has a fixed maturity or a fixed interest or dividend, if all of the following apply:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A default has not occurred during the current fiscal year or within the three previous fiscal years or during the existence of the issuer and any predecessor if less than three fiscal years, in the payment of principal, interest, or dividends on the security.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The issuer is engaged in business, is not in the organizational stage or in bankruptcy or receivership, and is not and has not been within the previous twelve months a blank check, blind pool, or shell company that has no specific business plan or purpose or has indicated that its primary business plan is to engage in a merger or combination of the business with, or an acquisition of, an unidentified person.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{6.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E9_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E9_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Unsolicited brokerage transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nonissuer transaction by or through a broker-dealer registered or exempt from registration under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ effecting an unsolicited order or offer to purchase.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{7.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E1_30_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E1_30_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Nonissuer transaction by pledgees.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nonissuer transaction executed by a bona fide pledgee without the purpose of evading }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{8.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E11_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E11_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Nonissuer transactions with federal covered investment advisers.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nonissuer transaction by a federal covered investment adviser with investments under management in excess of one hundred million dollars acting in the exercise of discretionary authority in a signed record for the account of others.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{9.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E12_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E12_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Specified exchange transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A transaction in a security, whether or not the security or transaction is otherwise exempt, in exchange for one or more bona fide outstanding securities, claims, or property interests, or partly in such exchange and partly for cash, if the terms and conditions of the issuance and exchange or the delivery and exchange and the fairness of the terms and conditions have been approved after a hearing by a court; by an official or agency of the United States; by a state securities, banking, or insurance agency; or by any other government authority expressly authorized by law to grant such approvals.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{10.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E13_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E13_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Underwriter transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A transaction between the issuer or other person on whose behalf the offering is made and an underwriter, or among underwriters.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{11.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E14_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E14_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Unit secured transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A transaction in a note, bond, debenture, or other evidence of indebtedness secured by a mortgage or other security agreement if all of the following apply:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The note, bond, debenture, or other evidence of indebtedness is offered and sold with the mortgage or other security agreement as a unit.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A general solicitation or general advertisement of the transaction is not made.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A commission or other remuneration is not paid or given, directly or indirectly, to a person not registered under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ as a broker-dealer or as an agent.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{12.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E15_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E15_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Bankruptcy, guardian, or conservator transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A transaction by an executor, administrator of an estate, sheriff, marshal, receiver, trustee in bankruptcy, guardian, or conservator.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{13.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E16_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E16_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Transactions with specified investors.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A sale or offer to sell to any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An institutional investor.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A federal covered investment adviser.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Any other person exempted by rule adopted or order issued under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A person or class of persons who are granted this exemption by the administrator. The administrator, by rule or order, may grant this exemption to a person or class of persons based upon the factors of financial sophistication, net worth, and the amount of assets under investment.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{14.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E17_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E17_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Limited offering transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A sale or an offer to sell securities by or on behalf of an issuer, if the transaction is part of a single issue in which all of the following apply:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Not more than thirty-five purchasers are present in this state during any twelve consecutive months, other than those designated in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{subsection 13}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A general solicitation or general advertising is not made in connection with the offer to sell or sale of the securities.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A commission or other remuneration is not paid or given, directly or indirectly, to a person other than a broker-dealer registered under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or an agent registered under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ for soliciting a prospective purchaser in this state.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The issuer reasonably believes that all the purchasers in this state, other than those designated in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{subsection 13}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, are purchasing for investment.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{15.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E18_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E18_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Transactions with existing security holders.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A transaction under an offer to existing security holders of the issuer, including persons that at the date of the transaction are holders of convertible securities, options, or warrants, if a commission or other remuneration, other than a standby commission, is not paid or given, directly or indirectly, for soliciting a security holder in this state.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{16.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E19_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E19_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Offerings registered under }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and the }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An offer to sell, but not a sale, of a security not exempt from registration under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ if all of the following apply:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A registration or offering statement or similar record as required under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ has been filed, but is not effective, or the offer is made in compliance with rule 165 adopted under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{17 C.F.R. \'a7230.165}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A stop order of which the offeror is aware has not been issued against the offeror by the administrator or the securities and exchange commission, and an audit, inspection, or proceeding that is public and that may culminate in a stop order is not known by the offeror to be pending.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{17.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E2_30_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E2_30_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Offerings when registration has been filed, but is not effective under }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and exempt from the }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An offer to sell, but not a sale, of a security exempt from registration under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ if all of the following apply:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A registration statement has been filed under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, but is not effective.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A solicitation of interest is provided in a record to offerees in compliance with a rule adopted by the administrator under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A stop order of which the offeror is aware has not been issued by the administrator under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and an audit, inspection, or proceeding that may culminate in a stop order is not known by the offeror to be pending.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{18.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E21_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E21_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Control transactions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A transaction involving the distribution of the securities of an issuer to the security holders of another person in connection with a merger, consolidation, exchange of securities, sale of assets, or other reorganization to which the issuer, or its parent or subsidiary and the other person, or its parent or subsidiary, are parties.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{19.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E22_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E22_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Rescission offers.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A rescission offer, sale, or purchase under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 502.510}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{20.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E23_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E23_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Out-of-state offers or sales.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An offer or sale of a security to a person not a resident of this state and not present in this state if the offer or sale does not constitute a violation of the laws of the state or foreign jurisdiction in which the offeree or purchaser is present and is not part of an unlawful plan or scheme to evade }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{21.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E24_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E24_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Employee benefit plans.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Employees\u8217\'3f stock purchase, savings, option, profit-sharing, pension, or similar employees\u8217\'3f benefit plan, including any securities, plan interests, and guarantees issued under a compensatory benefit plan or compensation contract, contained in a record, established by the issuer, its parents, its majority-owned subsidiaries, or the majority-owned subsidiaries of the issuer\u8217\'3fs parent for the participation of their employees including offers or sales of such securities to any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Directors; general partners; trustees, if the issuer is a business trust; officers; consultants; and advisers.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Family members who acquire such securities from those persons through gifts or domestic relations orders.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Former employees, directors, general partners, trustees, officers, consultants, and advisers if those individuals were employed by or providing services to the issuer when the securities were offered.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Insurance agents who are exclusive insurance agents of the issuer, or the issuer\u8217\'3fs subsidiaries or parents, or who derive more than fifty percent of their annual income from those organizations.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{22.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E25_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E25_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Specified dividends and tender offers and judicially recognized reorganizations.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A transaction involving any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A stock dividend or equivalent equity distribution, whether the corporation or other business organization distributing the dividend or equivalent equity distribution is the issuer or not, if nothing of value is given by stockholders or other equity holders for the dividend or equivalent equity distribution other than the surrender of a right to a cash or property dividend if each stockholder or other equity holder may elect to take the dividend or equivalent equity distribution in cash, property, or stock.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An act incident to a judicially approved reorganization in which a security is issued in exchange for one or more outstanding securities, claims, or property interests, or partly in such exchange and partly for cash.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The solicitation of tenders of securities by an offeror in a tender offer in compliance with rule 162 adopted under the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{17 C.F.R. \'a7230.162}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{23.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E26_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E26_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Nonissuer transactions involving specified foreign issuer securities traded on designated security exchanges.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A nonissuer transaction in an outstanding security by or through a broker-dealer registered or exempt from registration under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, if the issuer is a reporting issuer in a foreign jurisdiction designated by }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or by rule adopted or order issued under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; has been subject to continuous reporting requirements in the foreign jurisdiction for not less than one hundred eighty days before the transaction; and the security is listed on the foreign jurisdiction\u8217\'3fs securities exchange that has been designated by }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ or by rule adopted or order issued under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or is a security of the same issuer that is of senior or substantially equal rank to the listed security or is a warrant or right to purchase or subscribe to any of the foregoing. For purposes of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, Canada, together with its provinces and territories, is a designated foreign jurisdiction and the Toronto stock exchange, inc., is a designated securities exchange. After an administrative hearing in compliance with }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 17A}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the administrator, by rule adopted or order issued under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, may revoke the designation of a securities exchange under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, if the administrator finds that revocation is necessary or appropriate in the public interest and for the protection of investors.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{24.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Intrastate crowdfunding.}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E2_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E2_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Definitions.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{As used in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, unless the context otherwise requires:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fIntermediary\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(a)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A broker-dealer that is subject to the registration requirements of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 502.401}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and that facilitates the offer and sale of securities by issuers to investors through an internet-based system that is open to and accessible by the general public.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(b)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A business entity that is all of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(i)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A funding portal that is registered with the securities and exchange commission pursuant to the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Act of 1933}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, including as provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{15 U.S.C. \'a777d-1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(ii)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A member of the financial industry regulatory authority, inc. pursuant to the }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Exchange Act of 1934}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, including as provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{15 U.S.C. \'a7\'a778c and 78o-3}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, and }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf1{17 C.F.R. \'a7227.400}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(c)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A business entity that qualifies as an Iowa crowdfunding portal by meeting all of the following requirements:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(i)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Is registered with the administrator as required by the administrator.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(ii)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Is engaged in intrastate crowdfunding offers and sales of exempt securities in this state through an internet site.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(iii)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Does not operate or facilitate a secondary market in securities. }}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fIntrastate crowdfunding\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means the offer or sale of a security by an issuer in a transaction that is available for purchase only by an Iowa resident or a business entity having its principal place of business in this state.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E3_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E3_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Exemption not available.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The exemption in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ is not available to any of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A foreign issuer.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An investment company, as defined in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 3 of the federal Investment Company Act of 1940}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A development stage company that either has no specific business plan or purpose or has indicated that the company\u8217\'3fs business plan is to engage in a merger or acquisition with an unidentified company or companies, or other entity or person.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(4)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A company with a class of securities registered under the federal }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities Exchange Act of 1934}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(5)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Any person who is subject to a disqualifying event as described in the regulations adopted in accordance with }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 926 of the federal Dodd-Frank Wall Street Reform and Consumer Protection Act, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Pub. L. No. 111-203}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or in rules adopted by the administrator pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 17A}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E4_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E4_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Aggregate sales limit.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The aggregate amount of securities sold to all investors by the issuer during the twelve-month period preceding the date of the offer or sale, including any amount sold in reliance upon the exemption in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, shall not exceed five million dollars other than either of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities sold to Iowa resident institutional investors.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Securities sold to the Iowa resident issuer\u8217\'3fs management.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E5_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E5_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Individual sales limit.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The aggregate amount of securities sold to an investor by the issuer during the twelve-month period preceding the date of the offer or sale, including any amount sold in reliance upon the exemption in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, shall not exceed five thousand dollars unless the investor is an accredited investor who resides in Iowa. For purposes of this individual sales limit, the following investors shall be treated as one investor:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A relative, spouse, or relative of the spouse of an investor who has the same principal residence as the investor.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A trust or estate in which an investor and any related person collectively have more than fifty percent of the beneficial interest, excluding contingent interests.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{A corporation or other organization of which an investor and any related person collectively are beneficial owners of more than fifty percent of the equity securities, excluding directors\u8217\'3f qualifying shares, or equity interests.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{e.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E6_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E6_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Use of an intermediary.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{All offers and sales of securities made in reliance upon the exemption in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall be made through an intermediary\u8217\'3fs internet site.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{f.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E7_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E7_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Notice to administrator.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Prior to the offer of any security in this state made in reliance upon the exemption in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the issuer shall file a notice with the administrator in a form and format approved by the administrator, and including the filing fee specified by rule, if any.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{g.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E8_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E6_2E3_2E27_2E8_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Rulemaking.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The administrator shall adopt all rules necessary to implement the exemption in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ including but not limited to all of the following:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Mandatory disclosures.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Restrictions on advertising and communications.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Target amount, offering period, and escrow requirements.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(4)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Use and compensation of promoters.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(5)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Restrictions on the sale of securities purchased under the exemption in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(6)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Sales reports.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(7)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Limitations on the offering price.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(8)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Duties of an intermediary which shall include providing the administrator with continuous investor-level access to the intermediary\u8217\'3fs internet site. }}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(9)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Records maintenance.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(10)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Duties and registration requirements for internet site operators.}}}\par}{}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{[SS15, \'a71920-u1; C24, 27, \'a78526; C31, 35, \'a78581-c4; C39, \'a7}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{8581.04;}}}{ C46, 50, 54, 58, 62, \'a7502.4; C66, 71, 73, 75, \'a7496B.18, 502.4; C77, 79, \'a7496B.18, 502.202; }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{C81, \'a7502.202