xchange commission, or a self-regulatory organization. Upon request from a federal covered investment adviser and for good cause, the administrator, by order issued, may waive, in whole or in part, the application of the requirements of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ to the investment adviser representative.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{6.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E9_2E5_2E8_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E9_2E5_2E8_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Referral fees.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{An investment adviser registered under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, a federal covered investment adviser that has filed a notice under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 502.405}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or a broker-dealer registered under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ is not required to employ or associate with an individual as an investment adviser representative if the only compensation paid to the individual for a referral of investment advisory clients is paid to an investment adviser registered under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, a federal covered investment adviser who has filed a notice under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 502.405}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or a broker-dealer registered under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ with whom the individual is employed or associated as an investment adviser representative.}}}\par}{}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{[C77, 79, }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{81, \'a7502.404}}}{]}\par}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{83 Acts, ch 169, \'a714}}}{; }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{97 Acts, ch 23, \'a760}}}{; }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2004 Acts, ch 1161, \'a729, 68}}}{; }{{\f5\fs18\hyphp